Instructions for installing Ubuntu (Server):

1. Select VDI
2. Select Language "English"
3. Select "English" again
4. Select country "United States"
5. Dectect Keyboard? Select "yes"
6. Press the keys as instructed
7. To determine your keyboard type, if you have $ symbol press it. 

Setup:
8. Type a hostname "foo"
9. Type a username "bar"
10. Type account name "team1"
11. Type a password "..."
12. Re-enter the same password
13. Encrypt files? Select "no"
14. Partition: Select "Guided Use Entire Disk"
15. Write choice? Select "yes"

-Now it installs base system-
16. Config package manage? Leave blank, Select "continue"
17. Updates? Select "No auto updates"
18. Software selection? Select "open ssh server"
19. Install GRUB boot? Select "no"
20. Type "/dev/sda", Select "continue"
21. Select "Finish"